1947;;The White Unicorn;;British;;Bernard Knowles;;Margaret Lockwood, Joan Greenwood;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_White_Unicorn;;At a home for delinquent girls, a troublesome girl (Joan Greenwood), swaps reminiscences with the warden (Margaret Lockwood), who recounts her own unhappy marriage, divorce and tragic death of her second husband.[4]